dc_title_s: Lacus Lemani vicinorumque locorum nova et accurata descriptio.; Lacvs lemani vicinorvmq locorvm nova et accvrata descriptio
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Includes the inscription "Benevole lector F. Franciam, G. Genevam de notat. Haec volebam nescius ne esses. Vale et nostros conatus boni consule" and illustrations of ships and sea monsters on Lake Geneva. From the Composite Atlas of France, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map 35 x 47 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: Vignaud, Henry, 1830-1922, former owner, Composite Atlas of France.
